source.name: Geochemistry of Water Samples in the US from the NURE-HSSR Database
source.description: Geochemical analyses of water samples throughout the U.S. collected by the hydrogeochemical and stream sediment reconnaissance (HSSR) phase of the National Uranium Resource Evaluation (NURE) program. This database contains 335,547 records.
